Sentencas: Perovskite type La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 powders were prepared via simple polyol method for the first time in literature.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 electrolyte by polyol method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Obtained material was characterized by using XRD, SEM, Impedance Spectroscopy and density measurements.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 electrolyte by polyol method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Pure LSGM powders were achieved after heat treatment at 1100 degrees C for 12 h. 87% relative density was obtained after pressing of these powders under 1 MPa and sintering at 1250 degrees C for 12 h. Average particle size was calculated as 1.77-2.4 pal from SEM micrographs.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 electrolyte by polyol method for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Overall conductivity of the LSGM pellet was found to be 0.0014 S/cm at 850 degrees C with impedance analysis and showed that the preparation process needs improvements.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3 electrolyte by polyol method for solid oxide fuel cells
